Conagra Brands Logo Conagra Brands, Inc. is an American consumer packaged goods holding company headquartered in Chicago, Illinois. Conagra makes and sells products under various brand names that are available in supermarkets, restaurants, and food service establishments. As of September 2021 the company had a valuation in terms of its market capitalization of $16.4 billion. Source
